 going on in Maple World!\r\n\r\n[h1]Maple Mentor Event Winners[/h1]\r\n\r\nIn the latter half of June, [url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/discussion/45576/winners-maple-mentors-guide-creation]Kyrios issued a challenge to the veterans of MapleStory 2[/url]: Give newer players a leg up by crafting a guide to one of MapleStory 2's many features. The community came through and then some, creating dozens of guides that [url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/categories/player-guides]you can peruse on the Player Guides forums[/url], including explorations on Awakened Classes, Housing Tips, Mini-Game Guides and more!\r\n\r\nFour guides were selected as the best of the best, and you can check them out below!\r\n\r\n[h1]Gemstones & Socketing Guide[/h1]\r\n\r\n[url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/discussion/45691/mechanic-gemstones-socketing-guide][img]https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steamcommunity/public/images/clans/33702547/6597ad80fd8a0b5a56219848383380b0994151b1.png[/img][/url]\r\n\r\nSynkido from NA West takes on a full, detailed look at everything to do with upgrading and socketing gemstones, so that you can get the most out of your accessories. [url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/discussion/45691/mechanic-gemstones-socketing-guide]Take a look at the guide to boost your gemstones[/url]!\r\n\r\n[h1]The Fashionista's Guide[/h1]\r\n\r\n[url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/discussion/45638/lifestyle-the-fashionista-s-guide][img]https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steamcommunity/public/images/clans/33702547/d0d439c23013be2624d201c3df69a6cfa23b11f7.png[/img][/url]\r\n\r\nCynna from NA East unleashes the fashionista in all of us to go into the many ways you can find new outfits to give your character a unique look. [url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/discussion/45638/lifestyle-the-fashionista-s-guide]Get your own special look with the Fashionista's Guide today[/url]!\r\n\r\n[h1]L1-L3 Guild Raid Guide[/h1]\r\n\r\n[url=http://forums.maplestory2.nexon.net/d