mes, even encounters such as [b]Chaos Raids[/b], [b]Eye of Lapenta[/b], and [b]Cathy Mart[/b]! And don't worry about imposing on the veterans, because they get a special set of rewards for lending you a hand!\r\n\r\n[h1]An Enchanting Moment with Ophelia![/h1]\r\n\r\nWe here at the Tria Tribune got a special opportunity to catch up with Ophelia!\r\n\r\n[b]Tria Tribune:[/b] Hello, Ophelia! Thank you for speaking to us, how are y-\r\n\r\n[b]Ophelia:[/b] How am I? I'm angry, that's what I am! Do you know what they did to me?!\r\n\r\n[b]T:[/b] Uh, no? Sorry, is something wr-\r\n\r\n[b]Ophelia:[/b] Do you have any idea how great I had it? Only game in town, complete control of all of the Enchanting, and then [b]somebody[/b] had to go and show Peachy how to do the job right!\r\n\r\n[b]T:[/b] We, uh, we have some questions... are you enjoying any good restauran-\r\n\r\n[b]Ophelia:[/b] People were praying to me! They were begging me! Now a third of my customers have run off to that pretender and I'm suppose to act like it's no big deal?\r\n\r\n[b]T:[/b] Well, it was a little unfair-\r\n\r\n[b]Ophelia:[/b] Unfair?! Who cares about fair? Fair doesn't keep me swimming in Onyx Crystals! I swear, if I ever find this LAMBCOOK I'm going to show him what I really think of his 'New Leaf' cr-\r\n\r\n[b]T:[/b] WellthankyouverymuchOpheliaI'mafraidthat'sallthetimewehave!\r\n\r\n[h1]July Art Corner[/h1]\r\n\r\n[img]https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steamcommunity/public/images/clans/33702547/ca092b3f0ceaf8ad3faa389db54d63b01d6f0905.png[/img]\r\n\r\nMapleStory 2 has tons of talented artists, sharing their creations both through UGCs and through fan art. Many have also submitted their art works to the MapleStory team, and for the last few months we have been showing off their gorgeous works with the bi-weekly Art Corner posts. If you'd like your own creations featured, [url=https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfjFmbSkdRBIwG2JHUZf3Y5eDVz7PdL-r7a_ioqNkxdtqXtaA/viewform]submit your creation