g and from the Twisted Pocket Realm when opening Turka's Cache, while additional [b]Lucky Golden Keys[/b] can be found by defeating Lv. 10 and higher Elite Monsters and opening the Wooden and Golden Treasure Chests hidden throughout Maple World! Open up 200 [b]Lucky Boxes[/b] for a special set of bonus prizes, including a unique title, [b]Legendary Toad's Toolkits[/b] and [b]Legendary Armor Bonus Value Re-Rollers[/b]!\r\n\r\n[b]Event Duration[/b]: End of Maintenance, Thursday, July 25th - Start of Maintenance, Thursday, August 29th\r\n\r\n[b]Event Details[/b]:\r\n[list]\r\n[*]Log into MapleStory 2 every day to claim the following:[list]\r\n[*][b]2x Lucky Boxes[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]2x Lucky Golden Keys[/b][/*]\r\n[/list][/*]\r\n[*]You can use a [b]Lucky Golden Key[/b] to open a [b]Lucky Box[/b], which contains one of a variety of useful resources and consumables[/*]\r\n[*]You can earn additional [b]Lucky Boxes[/b] through various activities within MapleStory 2:[list]\r\n[*]Completing a Mini-Game: 100% chance to earn a [b]Lucky Box[/b][/*]\r\n[*]Fishing: 1% chance per catch to earn a [b]Lucky Box[/b][/*]\r\n[*]Performing: 1% chance per 15 seconds to earn a [b]Lucky Box[/b][/*]\r\n[*]Twisted Pocket Realm: 10% change to loot a [b]Lucky Box[/b] from Turka's Cache[/*]\r\n[*]Twisted Pocket Realm: 50% change to loot a [b]Lucky Box[/b] from Turka's Rare Cache[/*]\r\n[*]You can earn up to 40 additional Lucky Boxes per week[/*]\r\n[/list][/*]\r\n[*]You can also earn additional [b]Lucky Golden Keys[/b]:[list]\r\n[*]Defeating Lv. 10 or higher Elite Monsters has a 10% chance of awarding a [b]Lucky Golden Key[/b][/*]\r\n[*]Opening a Wooden Treasure Chest has a 20% chance of awarding a [b]Lucky Golden Key[/b][/*]\r\n[*]Opening a Golden Treasure Chest has a 100% chance of awarding a [b]Lucky Golden Key[/b][/*]\r\n[/list][/*]\r\n[*]Open up 200 Lucky Boxes to complete the \"Luck On Your Side\" quest and earn a set of bonus prizes![list]\r\n[*][b]\"Bling Bling\" Title[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]30,000 Onyx Crystals[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]3x Legendary Toad's Toolkits[/b] (expires 12:00 AM UTC, Sept. 1st), which can be used in place of Catalysts when enchanting[/*]\r\n[*][b]3x Heavy Lapenshard Boxes[/b], which contains the following Lapenshards:[list]\r\n[*][b]Sword of Time Red Lapenshard (Tier 1)[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]Eupheria's Protection Green Lapenshard (Tier 1)[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]Space Rift Blue Lapenshard (Tier 1)[/b] for the job of the character that opened the box[/*]\r\n[/list][/*]\r\n[*][b]2x Legendary Armor Bonus Value Re-Rollers[/b] (expires 12:00 AM UTC, Sept. 1st)[/*]\r\n[/list][/*]\r\n[/list]\r\n[b]Event Details[/b]\r\n [i]Each Lucky Box contains one of the following, selected randomly[/i]:\r\n[list]\r\n[*][b]5x Elixirs[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]10x Chaos Onyx Crystals[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]1,000x Onyx Crystals[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]100x Crystal Fragments[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]5x Red Crystals[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]5x Blue Crystals[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]5x Green Crystals[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]10x Special Warrior Tonic[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]10x Special Health Tonic[/b][/*]\r\n[*][b]10x Special Mage Tonic[/b][/*]\r\n[/list]\r\n[h1]Patch Day Login Event[/h1]\r\n\r\nJoin us on the first day of the new patch to collect a special bonus to start off your Lucky Box fun fast: [b]5 Lucky Boxes and Lucky Keys[/b]! You'll need to login before 3:30 PM UTC on Friday, July 26th in order to get these bonuses, so be sure to hurry in once the maintenance ends!\r\n\r\n[b]Event Duration[/b]:\r\n[list]\r\n[*][b]UTC[/b]: End of Maintenance, Thursday, July 25th - 3:30 PM Friday, July 26th[/*]\r\n[*][b]PDT (UTC -7)[/b]: End of Maintenance, Thursday, July 25th - 8:30 AM, Friday, July 26th[/*]\r\n[*][b]EDT (UTC -4)[/b]: End of Maintenance, Thursday, July 25th - 11:30 AM, Friday, July 26th[/*]\r\n[*][b]BRT (UTC -3)[/b]: End of Maintenance, Thursday, July 25th - 12:30 PM, Friday, July 26th[/*]\r\n[*][b]CEST (UTC +2)[/b]: End of Maintenance, Thursday, July 25th - 5:30 PM Friday, July 26th[/*]\r\n[*][b]AEST (UTC +10)[/b]: End of Main